China Minsheng Bank to Issue Up to 20 Billion Yuan Conv. Bonds

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-02-25T11:32:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-25/china-minsheng-bank-to-issue-up-to-20-billion-yuan-conv-bonds.html
China Minsheng Banking Corp. said it
cancelled a plan to issue A-shares in a placement in Shanghai
and will instead issue as much as 20 billion yuan in convertible
bonds in  Shanghai .  The bank will also issue new H-shares in Hong Kong, the
company said in a statement to the Hong Kong stock exchange
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nerys Avery at 
 navery2@bloomberg.net  